{"tid":1560503,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Rambo 5 : Last Blood  第一滴血：終極血戰","createTime":"2019-09-11T08:25:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T02:20:57.000Z","uid":184679,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"71d1bc8f9bfe25d017804b292e19b5acb1240072","tid":1560503,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T08:25:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://assets.wmoov.com/movie/photo/201905/FB_IMG_1559226290879_1559230192.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.wmoov.com%2Fmovie%2Fphoto%2F201905%2FFB_IMG_1559226290879_1559230192.jpg&h=98227425&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n演員<br />\n史泰龍<br />\n<br />\n語言<br />\n英語<br />\n<br />\n級別<br />\nTBC<br />\n<br />\n導演<br />\n阿祖安格朗堡<br />\n<br />\n類型<br />\n動作、劇情<br />\n<br />\n語言 :<br />\n    英語 (中文字幕)<br />\n<br />\n上映 :<br />\n    19.9.2019 (公映) <br />\n<br />\n故事簡介<br />\n相隔37年，史泰龍《第一滴血》經典系列的最終章！<br />\n<br />\n莊蘭保退隱農場，平日專注養馬及照顧鄰居，遠離一切煩擾及紛爭。一日，友人的女兒嘉布娜希望到墨西哥尋找親父。莊認為太危險，屢次阻撓但不成功，嘉布娜於是偷偷地獨自前往墨西哥。可惜，嘉布娜被朋友出賣，賣身給當地的黑幫賣淫集團，遭受折磨凌辱！<br />\n<br />\n莊蘭保得知後，馬上前往墨西哥拯救嘉布娜，但一切已太遲&hellip;&hellip;莊身受重傷，幸得一名獨立記者出手相救。莊康復後，單人匹馬直闖黑幫陣地報復！黑幫暴徒追趕至莊的農場，與莊埋身肉搏，展開最後一場終極血戰！ <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v81oO1gPmYc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dv81oO1gPmYc&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWWWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=9ceb2cf1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v81oO1gPmYc</a>"},{"pid":"d86c40365373cac1f2e4bfd0a7cd3972cff20ce7","tid":1560503,"uid":84869,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T08:26:21.000Z","msg":"重有幾多滴血"},{"pid":"a31198cc6211c95ee0a21461df3ec6aa4613ad3f","tid":1560503,"uid":35451,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T09:22:51.000Z","msg":"劇情好似taken咁既"},{"pid":"c1d5999d1c173d87e558d7605b405f7fe9ebf146","tid":1560503,"uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pi